Lever,is,a,collaborative,applicant,tracking,system,and,hiring,platform,The,platform,integrates,with,email,to,improve,communication,and,make,it,easy,to,request,feedback,on,a,candidate,Coworkers,can,be,more,involved,with,sourcing,and,referrals,The,Lever,Postings,API,allows,users,to,programmatically,retrieve,job,postings,for,their,company,get,postings,that,match,a,given,query,get,individual,postings,by,ID,and,apply,to,a,job,posting,The,API,does,not,allow,full,text,searches,for,open,jobs,does,not,support,CORS,headers,for,job,postings,on,exterior,domains,and,does,not,provide,a,unique,iframe,for,job,details